<concept id="concept_ufm_5yv_m3c">
    <title>5. Testing Strategy</title>
    <conbody>
        <p>Testing will include:</p>
        <section id="section_swr_vyv_m3c">
            <title>Unit Tests</title>
            <p>Components to test:</p>
            <pre>markdown parsing
chunk generation
similarity calculations</pre>
        </section>
        <section id="section_twr_vyv_m3c">
            <title>Integration Tests</title>
            <p>Test full pipeline:</p>
            <pre>query → retrieval → LLM → response</pre>
        </section>
        <section id="section_uwr_vyv_m3c">
            <title>Manual Testing</title>
            <p>Example queries:</p>
            <ul id="ul_kwj_wyv_m3c">
                <li>What automation tools have you built?</li>
                <li>What is create-kb-met?</li>
                <li>Explain your metadata pipeline.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section id="section_x4h_wnd_w3c">
            <title>Additional validation:</title>
            <ul id="ul_qz1_ynd_w3c">
                <li>
                    <p>intent classification accuracy</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>metadata influence on retrieval ranking</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>comparison queries (multi-document reasoning)</p>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </conbody>
</concept>
